name: As The Grove Coalesce
description:
For some of us, new year cycles means new beginnings. We wrote our dreams, hopes, and held on to our faith as we fight to survive the year.  
 
Last year, we somehow learned that being a part of a healthy community is actually very important to our growth-- whether for our art or ourselves as a person.  
 
Watching each and every one of us learn and grow together became quite a wholesome experience. And as we coalesce, we carry each other with the same objective: We Are Gonna Make It. Let's survive this year!

Artist: Jemala 
Title: As The Grove Coalesce
Format: 44,1Khz 16bit Stereo WAV File 
Duration: 02:27
